  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个时序图，描述用户提交站点URL后的完整处理流程。核心是从HTTP请求开始，经过消息队列，最终触发实际的站点更新检查。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "HTTPHandler",
        "PubSub",
        "EventHandler",
        "CheckSiteForUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为：User发起请求，HTTPHandler接收，然后交给PubSub做异步解耦，EventHandler消费消息，最后调用CheckSiteForUpdate执行实际逻辑。这样分层对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "HTTPHandler",
        "PubSub",
        "EventHandler",
        "CheckSiteForUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，关键是PubSub到EventHandler这一步要用虚线箭头，表示是消息投递的异步回调，不是同步调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PubSub",
        "EventHandler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把五个参与者都列出来：User、HTTPHandler、PubSub、EventHandler、CheckSiteForUpdate。然后画User到HTTPHandler的POST请求，标注上`POST request /<site_url`。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "HTTPHandler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "HTTPHandler收到请求后不要直接处理，而是发消息给PubSub，标注为`Publish message`。这里要注意是同步调用，用实线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTPHandler",
        "PubSub"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。接下来是PubSub到EventHandler的虚线箭头，标注`Deliver message`。然后EventHandler到CheckSiteForUpdate的调用，我暂时标成`Call to handle event`，可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PubSub",
        "EventHandler",
        "CheckSiteForUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "EventHandler到CheckSiteForUpdate的箭头方向反了，应该是EventHandler指向CheckSiteForUpdate，表示EventHandler主动调用它。另外确认一下，EventHandler和CheckSiteForUpdate之间是同步调用吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventHandler",
        "CheckSiteForUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在方向正确了：EventHandler - CheckSiteForUpdate，实线箭头，标注`Call to handle event`。整个流程已经完整：User POST请求 → HTTPHandler发布消息 → PubSub投递 → EventHandler调用 → CheckSiteForUpdate执行更新检查。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "HTTPHandler",
        "PubSub",
        "EventHandler",
        "CheckSiteForUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个时序图准确反映了我们系统的异步架构。PubSub的引入让HTTPHandler可以快速响应，实际的重活交给后台的CheckSiteForUpdate慢慢处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTPHandler",
        "PubSub",
        "CheckSiteForUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
